[size=3][spoiler]Ever wish Minecraft had turn-based combat? Or that you could play chess in Minecraft? Or that I would stop opening these articles with rhetorical questions and just get to the point for once? All these things are possible, and so much more, now that scripting API is available in the Minecraft public beta![/spoiler]想让 Minecraft 里的战斗变为回合制，或是想在 Minecraft 里下棋？或者是让我别再废话直接切入正题？现在，有了脚本 API，一切皆有可能。

[spoiler]But what is scripting API (Application Programming Interface)? Essentially, it's the art of tweaking a game’s insides – writing new commands into Minecraft's texty innards to modify the game. The Minecraft Script Engine uses the JavaScript language. Scripts can be written and bundled with Behaviour Packs to listen and respond to game events, get (and modify) data in components that entities have, and affect different parts of the game.[/spoiler]不过，什么是脚本 API（应用程序接口）呢？简单来讲，它是一种让你修改游戏内部的艺术——向 Minecraft 的核心添入新的命令来修改游戏。[b]Minecraft 脚本引擎[/b]使用 [b]JavaScript[/b] 语言。写好的脚本可以放到[b]行为包[/b]中，它能够监听并响应游戏事件、获取（与编辑）实体拥有的组件数据，以及影响游戏的很多部分。

