[spoiler]Minecraft: Java Edition players have been modding the game since forever, and this is our first step to creating a similar setup for Minecraft players on other platforms! Currently, it's only a feature that Minecraft beta players on Windows 10 can access (and you can learn more about how to sign up for that beta by clicking this line of green text).[/spoiler]Minecraft Java 版的玩家很早以前就可以给游戏写 Mod 了，脚本 API 是我们为其他平台的 Minecraft 玩家创造相似的体验的第一步。目前，它只能被 Windows 10 上的 beta 玩家使用（你可以[url=https://minecraft.net/en-us/article/how-get-minecraft-betas]点击这个链接来了解如何注册 beta 版[/url]）。

